fg_segments: This is the website of CalculatorSoup.com, Owned and operated by CalculatorSoup, LLC.
We can be reached via email at ed at calculatorsoup dot com or by telephone at 508-231-1331 or, by our postal address:CalculatorSoup, LLCPO Box 131Ashland, MA 01721
By using this site you agree to its privacy policy and use of cookies.
In general, we may receive the following information from users.
Personal Information: In the form of return email addresses when a user sends electronic correspondence to us requesting specific information or to make a comment or request a calculator.
We use this information only to respond to these requests.
Aggregated Server Information: Information about users as a whole.
CalculatorSoup, LLC receives certain types of information about general website traffic at CalculatorSoup.com.

This does not include personally-identifying information, but does include visit frequency, which pages are visited, which search terms are used, what domain names (e.g., "google.com" or "facebook.com") visitors are coming from and the date and time of each visit.
CalculatorSoup, LLC gathers and compiles this information into an aggregate form for web traffic analysis.
This analysis is related to website activity overall rather than on an individual level and does not include personally-identifiable information.
Because aggregated information does not include personally-identifying information, it cannot be used to identify you.
We may disclose aggregated website traffic data to third parties, such as advertisers, or include it in public records.
IP Addresses: When a user submits a contact form, their IP address is recorded in the email that gets sent to CalculatorSoup, LLC.

Also, when an error occurs in a website script (e.g. a calculator) an error message is sent to CalculatorSoup, LLC support email address with details regarding that error along with the origin IP address which in most cases is the user's IP address.
CalculatorSoup, LLC uses IP addresses, only if necessary, for the sole purpose of combating Spamming and Hacking.

Cookies used by CalculatorSoup.com With respect to cookies: We use cookies to track user preferences on CalculatorSoup.com, for example, date and currency formats, or cookie consent however, all calculators remain functional even if you disable your cookies.
Third Party Advertising and Third Party Cookies With respect to Ad Servers:
When and if ads are present, we allow third-party companies to serve ads on our site pages.
These companies may use information about your visits to this and other websites in order to provide advertisements about goods and services of interest to you.
Third party vendors, including Google, use cookies to serve ads based on a user's prior visits to our website.
Google's use of cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads to our users based on their visits to our sites and/or other sites on the Internet.
You can find out more about Google's use of cookies by visiting Google's Privacy and Terms page.
You can opt out of a third-party vendor's use of cookies by visiting the Network Advertising Initiative opt-out page.
Website Analytics CalculatorSoup, LLC uses Google Analytics to analyze website traffic.
You can learn more about how Google uses data when you use their partners' sites or apps, How Google uses data.
If you feel that this site is not following its stated information privacy policy, you may contact us at the above email address, phone number or postal address. Last updated: July 1, 2017
